POPULAR cider Brutal Fruit has announced that they have launched a new fragrance. The brand, popularly known for alcohol, announced yesterday in a press statement that it was taking a spin and into cosmetics. The new fragrance is called ‘You Belong’ and is a delicate blend of fruity, floral and spicy notes. “Our new fragrance is the head turner you never knew you needed ???? Introducing You Belong by Brutal Fruit: An elegant and delicate blend of fruity, floral and spicy notes, inspired by confident women. Is this exciting or what? Comment below if you’d like to try it.” The brand posted on their Instagram post. A post shared by Brutal Fruit (@brutalfruitza)   “It may seem unexpected, a fragrance – but in actual fact, it makes perfect sense that we are fortunate enough to be able to bring our consumers such a unique offering, a scent which truly embodies and personifies that ’You Belong to Affect’. “We are so excited to share the ’You Belong’ fragrance with our South African consumers, and we hope that the narrative continues to resonate with everyone. “We stand firm in our mantra, and what better way to affect your entrance into a room or own a moment than with how you smell and how that scent makes you feel. The scent is simply incredible. We are very proud of this journey we are on,’ Ramona Kayembe, marketing manager of Brutal Fruit South Africa, said in a press statement. Details on merchandise distribution and price points are yet to be revealed.